Package: pwr
Type: Package
Title: pwr: an implementation of the Path-Weighted Regression Model for Networks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Calvo", "Ernesto", email = "ecalvo@umd.edu", role = c("cre", "aut")),
    person("Timoneda", "Joan", email = "joan.timoneda@gmail.com ", role = c("aut")), 
    person("Ventura", "Tiago", email="venturat@umd.edu", role=c("aut")))
Description: This packages implements the Path Weighted Local Regression (PWR) developed by Calvo, Timoneda e Ventura. 
    Inspired by the Geographically Weighted Regression Model,
    the PWR implements a fast and simple strategy to model data dependency on large networks.
